<p class="Normal" align="center"><img src="/upload/meohay/155/53357c407c468.jpg" alt="vong-tay-hat-1-538137-1371172422_500x0.j" border="1" /></p>
<p class="Normal" align="center">- D&acirc;y nến<br />- K&eacute;o cắt<br />- Hạt tr&ograve;n<br />- C&uacute;c &aacute;o</p>
<p class="Normal" align="center"><span>C&ugrave;ng l&agrave;m nh&eacute;:</span></p>
<p class="Normal">&nbsp;</p>
