</tr>
<tr>
<td><img src="/upload/meohay/155/53357c42d8611.jpg" alt="vong-tay-hat-8-710641-1371172460_500x0.j" border="1" /></td>
<td>
<p class="Normal"><span>Bước 5:</span></p>
<p class="Normal">Cuối c&ugrave;ng m&igrave;nh x&acirc;u c&uacute;c &aacute;o v&agrave;o để l&agrave;m kh&oacute;a c&agrave;i n&egrave;.</p>
